Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-------------------TEXT--------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.06,0:02:08.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年也承蒙您的关照了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.92,0:02:10.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请随意  请随意
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.61,0:02:12.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随便拿多少都行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.29,0:02:14.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.97,0:02:18.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了  自己挖的番薯自己拿
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.79,0:02:21.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能拿得多少就挖多少  我们说好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.63,0:02:24.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠鸠  快看  连在一起的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.84,0:02:26.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有这么大的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.82,0:02:30.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的呢  就像在寻宝一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.38,0:02:33.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛痛痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.05,0:02:37.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.27,0:02:38.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.27,0:02:42.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土…土鸠…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.05,0:02:45.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠鸠  屁股上都是泥巴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.75,0:02:49.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  那是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.50,0:02:56.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比艾草托儿所的孩子要大一些
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.61,0:02:59.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这家里的人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.95,0:03:03.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  这家的孙子已经是高中生了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.96,0:03:08.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…是谁家的孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.97,0:03:19.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  一个人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.14,0:03:22.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住在这附近吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.84,0:03:29.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.19,0:03:51.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  察觉到的时候已经晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.24,0:03:55.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  偶尔也会有人来小偷小摸的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.32,0:03:58.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是住在附近的孩子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.25,0:04:02.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  差不多该收拾收拾准备回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.05,0:04:04.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.92,0:04:06.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挖了好多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.10,0:04:08.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.64,0:04:11.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好多的番薯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.40,0:04:14.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.81,0:04:18.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  我一开始就说过了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.18,0:04:21.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己挖的自己拿
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.78,0:04:26.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  等回去了烤番薯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.00,0:04:30.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠鸠  你没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.84,0:04:33.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我帮你拿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.24,0:04:40.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题  我一个人搬得动
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.14,0:04:44.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都你自己拿太勉强了  我帮你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.56,0:04:49.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用  说好自己挖的番薯要自己拿
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.50,0:04:50.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是当然
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.02,0:04:54.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是欺负人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.47,0:05:03.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能  还是放弃吧  小鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.22,0:05:08.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姑娘  我来帮你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.02,0:05:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.36,0:05:12.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢您
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.81,0:05:19.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.56,0:05:21.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好呛人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.60,0:05:27.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烫吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.46,0:05:32.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.57,0:05:33.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.38,0:05:36.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很烫的要小心点哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.35,0:05:39.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.67,0:05:41.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.29,0:05:45.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.89,0:05:49.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些怎么处理
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.61,0:05:50.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.70,0:05:52.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还要再烤些吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.74,0:05:55.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分一些给街坊邻居吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.78,0:06:03.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤本  你能和小鸠一起去这些地方吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.67,0:06:07.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一个人去吧  那样更快些
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.91,0:06:10.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…不过还是一起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.76,0:06:15.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望她可以和街坊邻居相处得更融洽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.64,0:06:17.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗  小鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.62,0:06:18.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.19,0:06:24.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠会加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.51,0:06:28.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要求你帮忙  只求你别碍事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.73,0:06:35.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的番薯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.89,0:06:40.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是欺负人  老是叫我别碍事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.42,0:06:43.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是他没说「不要跟来」呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.96,0:06:49.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是番薯也被他抢走了  我本想自己分给大家的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.17,0:06:54.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也可以说成是「看起来很重  所以他来帮你拿」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.79,0:07:02.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.95,0:07:05.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是艾草托儿所的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.13,0:07:10.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们去挖番薯了  所以来分给大家一些美味的番薯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.71,0:07:13.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  谢谢你们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.00,0:07:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是艾草托儿所的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.98,0:07:21.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.45,0:07:24.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是番薯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.91,0:07:25.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.09,0:07:27.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是艾草托儿所的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.48,0:07:31.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤本先生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.35,0:07:32.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.76,0:07:37.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还差一点番薯就都分完了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.84,0:07:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.40,0:07:52.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀  欢迎回家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.75,0:07:53.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.49,0:07:58.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  小姑娘  好久不见了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.78,0:07:59.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.13,0:08:02.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牛奶  你过得还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.44,0:08:06.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长大了些呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.14,0:08:10.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  它过得很好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.38,0:08:17.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.75,0:08:24.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他路过这里时说他刚刚挖了番薯  想借点自来水洗手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.19,0:08:26.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙…是刚才的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.67,0:08:29.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿着这些  站住
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.67,0:08:37.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫你站住了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.33,0:08:39.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放手  小偷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.45,0:08:44.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我的台词  你这番薯贼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.20,0:08:46.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放我下来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.53,0:08:50.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤本先生  出什么事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.79,0:08:52.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小偷就要带去派出所
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.26,0:08:57.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  不要  我还给你  还给你就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.74,0:09:03.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然  离家出走吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.38,0:09:05.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离家出走？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.44,0:09:26.05,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.05,0:09:26.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫什么名字
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.74,0:09:32.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次选择沉默吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.81,0:09:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫什么名字
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.10,0:09:41.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫他番薯贼就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.24,0:09:43.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不是番薯贼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.14,0:09:48.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有名字的  对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.12,0:09:54.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,启太
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.24,0:10:00.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,启太你为什么要离家出走呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.92,0:10:04.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想去以前的家
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.85,0:10:06.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前的…家？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.63,0:10:09.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前住的房子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.90,0:10:13.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为母亲的公司换了  所以搬家了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.98,0:10:16.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  以前的家怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.98,0:10:22.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没去过
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.33,0:10:26.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在正要去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.40,0:10:29.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是想去…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.97,0:10:31.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘了在哪了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.67,0:10:33.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才没有忘
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.72,0:10:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  你脸上就是一副忘了的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.45,0:10:38.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.35,0:10:41.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己的家是不会忘记的  对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.92,0:10:47.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为…搬家的时候我才上幼儿园
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.66,0:10:49.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点搞不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.93,0:10:52.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就叫忘记了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.47,0:10:53.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才没有忘
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.09,0:10:59.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,启太  只要知道是什么样的房子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.13,0:11:02.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们或许可以帮你找找看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.44,0:11:05.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能画一下你的家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.57,0:11:08.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我能画
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.79,0:11:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个呀…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.72,0:11:17.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屋顶是红色的  在这里和这里有窗户
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.37,0:11:20.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里有天线  还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.66,0:11:23.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家附近的东西也都画画吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.87,0:11:26.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样找起来容易些
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.43,0:11:32.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里有个邮筒  隔壁有只狗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.21,0:11:39.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大的狗狗呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.62,0:11:41.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次经过那里它总朝我叫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.60,0:11:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（名字  吉村启太）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.17,0:11:57.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有还有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.05,0:12:01.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈经常做点心给我吃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.21,0:12:19.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还给我读画册  假期还带我去野营和游乐场
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.43,0:12:23.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,启太
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.65,0:12:28.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想回以前的家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.61,0:12:41.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤本先生  我想帮启太找他的家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.49,0:12:54.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,线索只有狗和邮筒的话  是不可能找到的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.10,0:12:58.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不起来别的什么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.77,0:13:15.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪边  右边还是左边？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.29,0:13:19.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…这边…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.68,0:13:21.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是这边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.72,0:13:42.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我知道这里  我来过的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.84,0:13:45.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  应该不远了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.81,0:13:48.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,启太  真是太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.35,0:13:48.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.19,0:14:05.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想喝吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.66,0:14:09.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是算了  不节约点的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.02,0:14:11.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,节约？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.02,0:14:14.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还知道这种难懂的词汇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.10,0:14:17.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为母亲时常叮嘱我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.51,0:14:19.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.95,0:14:21.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤本先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.39,0:14:27.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.55,0:14:28.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}（请随便拿）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.09,0:14:31.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是梨  一看便知吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.99,0:14:32.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接着
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.05,0:14:35.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.50,0:14:38.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为交换  把这个放在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.76,0:14:44.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.51,0:14:48.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.52,0:14:52.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤本也是有优点的  不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.85,0:14:56.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…要是一点也没有的话我会很困扰的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.67,0:14:58.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也给我梨吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.42,0:15:04.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.90,0:15:13.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非…这只狗是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.08,0:15:21.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说…这隔壁就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.19,0:15:37.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里不是我家…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.11,0:15:46.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.64,0:16:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让开
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.59,0:16:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的房间…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.25,0:16:20.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,锁着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.60,0:16:23.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只好打破了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.49,0:16:24.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤本先生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.48,0:16:30.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你…不要打破
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.25,0:16:41.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想回现在的家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.98,0:16:45.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为…有爷爷在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.05,0:16:47.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.79,0:16:49.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.36,0:16:54.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母亲和我  现在住在爷爷家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.83,0:16:58.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,启太讨厌爷爷吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.21,0:17:01.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为他老欺负人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.38,0:17:04.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欺负人…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.15,0:17:08.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.91,0:17:12.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一大早就叫我起来  吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.98,0:17:17.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  启太  快起来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.21,0:17:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点收拾好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.51,0:17:25.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上想多看会儿电视  还想打游戏来着
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.63,0:17:28.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,启太
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.64,0:17:30.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷  你做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.71,0:17:32.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不许熬夜  快点睡觉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.33,0:17:38.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃饭的时候也总让我吃些我不喜欢吃的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.71,0:17:40.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不喜欢吃的东西？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.64,0:17:43.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鱼啊  蔬菜什么的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.56,0:17:49.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,启太  不要浪费食物  给我好好吃饭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.59,0:17:53.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样就是欺负人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.46,0:17:56.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  爷爷讨厌我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.39,0:17:58.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以老是对我很苛刻
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.96,0:18:01.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他一定是希望我离开那个家
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.93,0:18:03.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以那种家…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.36,0:18:05.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,启太
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.47,0:18:11.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清花老师也经常对托儿所的孩子们说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.84,0:18:14.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「小鱼和蔬菜很有营养  所以一定要吃」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.12,0:18:16.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清花老师是？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.87,0:18:21.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清花老师是个很温柔  最喜欢小孩子的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.62,0:18:23.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾草托儿所的老师
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.23,0:18:26.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温柔？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.97,0:18:40.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,启太
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.63,0:18:48.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洗完澡快去睡觉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.34,0:19:00.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欺负人和没有欺负人是很难分辨的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.70,0:19:04.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但只要仔细观察还是能分清的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.34,0:19:10.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,启太  你原本是想在这里烤番薯吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.20,0:19:15.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前和大家一起烤番薯的时候  觉得很好吃  所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.09,0:19:20.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要负起责任  拿点回去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.33,0:19:24.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,农家的大婶那边我道过歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.59,0:19:29.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙挖太多了  剩下很多搬不动  于是跑掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.96,0:19:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,启太  真是太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.76,0:19:36.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.66,0:19:47.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的可以一个人回去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.87,0:19:49.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.54,0:19:53.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,启太  启太
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.88,0:20:00.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.84,0:20:04.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.76,0:20:12.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.97,0:20:21.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,启太
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.10,0:20:24.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.17,0:20:27.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,启太
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.62,0:20:33.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,启太
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.65,0:20:34.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.05,0:20:39.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛啊  你搞什么飞机啊  臭老头
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.42,0:20:42.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别老是让我操心  你这笨小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.86,0:20:44.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.85,0:20:48.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.40,0:20:55.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你母亲也在家里等你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.75,0:20:56.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.21,0:21:03.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,启太现在正和他爷爷一起上电车
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.61,0:21:05.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…没什么  再见
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.19,0:21:11.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤本先生知道启太家的电话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.53,0:21:14.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是藤本先生把启太的爷爷叫来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.46,0:21:15.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.03,0:21:17.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说这个了  我肚子饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.25,0:21:22.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去蒸番薯吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.29,0:21:25.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…好…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.98,0:21:26.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.55,0:21:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.21,0:21:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.06,0:21:34.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堂元先生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.35,0:21:36.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正要回去？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.75,0:21:38.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还有事先回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.44,0:21:41.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有事？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.95,0:21:44.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天托儿所组织去挖番薯了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.11,0:21:47.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后想分些给街坊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.81,0:21:50.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤本先生他…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.11,0:21:55.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实是个好人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.82,0:22:01.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  清和是个好人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.10,0:22:09.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是那个小鬼的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.95,0:22:13.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,启太看到以前的家时似乎很悲伤呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.15,0:22:18.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛  应该是因为理解了爷爷真正的心情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.50,0:22:21.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.57,0:22:25.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么…今天藤本那么努力…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.32,0:22:27.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,折半50分
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.73,0:22:32.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是早上藤本先生还欺负人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.30,0:22:35.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.55,0:22:37.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相抵一下  藤本0分
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.31,0:22:40.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对小鸠的努力给70分
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.24,0:22:44.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你擦干净以后再写上去嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.67,0:22:46.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛病真多啊你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.66,0:22:48.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是给你一半  50分好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.86,0:22:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你擦干净以后再…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.36,0:22:52.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了  25分
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.07,0:22:53.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.20,0:22:56.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不满啊？那就12.5分
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.65,0:22:59.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脸都漆黑一片啦
